com.isti.traceview.data
Class DataModule

java.lang.Object
  java.util.Observable
      com.isti.traceview.data.DataModule
Direct Known Subclasses:
XYZDataModule
public class DataModule
extends Observable

This class holds collections of events, stations, traces loaded from configured data sources. It provides a simplified interface to access data module functions.

Author:
Max Kokoulin
